[SPEAKER_00] znači,

182
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] 13. tjedan u Zagreb.

183
00:10:22,059 --> 00:10:23,620
[SPEAKER_02] Da,

184
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:25,039
[SPEAKER_02] i tu mi je doktor vidija,

185
00:10:25,039 --> 00:10:25,580
[SPEAKER_02] činje,

186
00:10:25,580 --> 00:10:27,179
[SPEAKER_02] uzeo papire i Splita,

187
00:10:27,179 --> 00:10:28,320
[SPEAKER_02] vidija je nalaze,

188
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,879
[SPEAKER_02] i rekao,

189
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:29,419
[SPEAKER_02] ova vam beba,

190
00:10:29,419 --> 00:10:30,840
[SPEAKER_02] svakako neće biti u redu,

191
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:33,799
[SPEAKER_02] najbolje bi vam bilo da vam se ovo iskomplicira

192
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:35,440
[SPEAKER_02] i da dobijete spontanika,

193
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,600
[SPEAKER_02] da se riješite toga.

194
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:41,340
[SPEAKER_02] Ali to je najžalostnija od svega,

195
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:43,340
[SPEAKER_02] što su to svi govorili meni.

196
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,700
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

197
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:47,179
[SPEAKER_02] niko nije se obratio njemu

198
00:10:47,179 --> 00:10:50,039
[SPEAKER_02] i niko nije to govorio kad je on bio sa mnom,

199
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,100
[SPEAKER_02] nego sve meni.

200
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:51,399
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

201
00:10:51,399 --> 00:10:53,460
[SPEAKER_02] trudnici koja je pod hormonima,

202
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:54,759
[SPEAKER_02] koja je ono,

203
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:56,259
[SPEAKER_02] prestrašena i ovako,

204
00:10:56,259 --> 00:10:58,840
[SPEAKER_02] i prestrašena.

205
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:01,440
[SPEAKER_02] I to još one na svetom duhu,

206
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:02,019
[SPEAKER_02] koji...

207
00:11:02,019 --> 00:11:02,179
[SPEAKER_02] Znači,

208
00:11:02,179 --> 00:11:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] bili smo tu u vašem susjedstvu,

209
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] u sveti duh klinika.

210
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,179
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su na to,

211
00:11:07,179 --> 00:11:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo bar tada prije čuli,

212
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:09,919
[SPEAKER_00] da su na glasu,

213
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:13,379
[SPEAKER_00] kao klinika koja ne radi abortuse,

214
00:11:13,379 --> 00:11:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] ali nas su normalno uredno savjetovali,

215
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,639
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da su savjetovali,

216
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:18,080
[SPEAKER_00] nego ono,

217
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] direkt u glavu,

218
00:11:20,019 --> 00:11:21,100
[SPEAKER_00] ovo neće biti u redu,

219
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] bolje vam se riješiti toga.

220
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

221
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:25,620
[SPEAKER_00] tim izrazov nije to bilo ni djete,

222
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] ni osoba,

223
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,200
[SPEAKER_00] ni plod,

224
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,200
[SPEAKER_00] nego to je bilo to u njihovom žargonu.

225
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, eto,

226
00:11:32,059 --> 00:11:34,259
[SPEAKER_00] to nas istavno malo razočaralo,

227
00:11:34,259 --> 00:11:36,080
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo bili u to nekom raskoraku.

228
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

229
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] znaš kako razmišljaš,

230
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] što ti vjera kaže.

231
00:11:42,679 --> 00:11:45,620
[SPEAKER_01] meni je teško slušati sad dok vi pričate,

232
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] a moli kako je se ona osjećala,

233
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:51,279
[SPEAKER_01] kad ti tako doktori kažu u paciju.

234
00:11:51,279 --> 00:11:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da, jer mi smo bili toliko zbunjeni,

235
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] s jedne strane,

236
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:54,879
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

237
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:56,379
[SPEAKER_00] savjesti govori jedno,

238
00:11:56,379 --> 00:11:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] pameti govori jedno,

239
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,919
[SPEAKER_00] struka,

240
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:00,940
[SPEAKER_00] svi,

241
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

242
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,240
[SPEAKER_00] svi lježnici,

243
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] neće biti dobro,

244
00:12:03,539 --> 00:12:04,419
[SPEAKER_00] to ne valja,

245
00:12:04,419 --> 00:12:05,779
[SPEAKER_00] to se treba riješiti,

246
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:07,700
[SPEAKER_00] čak ono,

247
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] ste vi svjesni u šta vi ulazite,

248
00:12:09,679 --> 00:12:11,120
[SPEAKER_00] šta to nosi sa sebom,

249
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:13,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao da smo mi bili čudni njima,

250
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] a te kasnije kad sam malo razmišljao,

251
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:20,039
[SPEAKER_00] sam stvari shvatio da koliko su oni vjerojatno

252
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:23,500
[SPEAKER_00] se susreću s tim slučajima gdje roditelji

253
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] pokreknu pred tim strafom za tu budućnost svoju,

254
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:30,179
[SPEAKER_00] možda to napraviti pod izlikom

255
00:12:30,179 --> 00:12:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] budućnosti djeteta,

256
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,220
[SPEAKER_00] kakav će on imati život,

257
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako će njemu biti,

258
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:36,899
[SPEAKER_00] u našem slučaju znači njemu,

259
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] a možda sve to pod izlikom

260
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:42,320
[SPEAKER_00] nekeg svoga komoda,

261
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] svoje sigurnosti u život,

262
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:47,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne prihvaćanja toga nekoga križa,

263
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,659
[SPEAKER_00] neke, da će nam tako,

264
00:12:49,659 --> 00:12:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] najznam križa cijeloživotnog, sigurno.

265
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:54,200
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da su vjerojatno oni bili,

266
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:57,620
[SPEAKER_00] više njima uskustva bilo da roditelji

267
00:12:57,620 --> 00:13:00,419
[SPEAKER_00] naprave to što struka savjetuje,

268
00:13:00,419 --> 00:13:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] nego da odbiju,

269
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,919
[SPEAKER_00] tako da su mi njima u stvari bili čudni

270
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] što smo odmah u statu jasno i glasno rekli

271
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,139
[SPEAKER_00] ne, mi nećemo to.

272
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:11,419
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko su oni vama dali vremena,

273
00:13:11,419 --> 00:13:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] nakon ti svi pregleda na kraj,

274
00:13:13,019 --> 00:13:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] kad se ustanovilo da djeti ima davnom sindrom,

275
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:18,740
[SPEAKER_01] koliko su vam dali vremena uopće da odlučite,

276
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:20,320
[SPEAKER_01] da se vas dvoje iskonsultirate,

277
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:22,399
[SPEAKER_01] da od tim šokom...

278
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:25,379
[SPEAKER_02] Nije bilo uopće govora o tome vremenu,

279
00:13:25,379 --> 00:13:28,299
[SPEAKER_02] jer znaš stav odmah od početka bio ne i gotovo.

280
00:13:28,299 --> 00:13:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] Da, niko od njih nije nas pitao nikad što vi želite,

281
00:13:32,159 --> 00:13:33,080
[SPEAKER_00] koja je vaša namjera,

282
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] nego njima je bilo znači i pretpostavka,

283
00:13:35,259 --> 00:13:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] djete ima sindrom,

284
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,639
[SPEAKER_00] ne valja,

285
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:38,620
[SPEAKER_00] pod navodnike,

286
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] rješavamo ga se.

287
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] Tako kada smo mi završili,

288
00:13:43,039 --> 00:13:45,480
[SPEAKER_00] poslije toga pregleda imali smo još jedan pregled

289
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:48,799
[SPEAKER_00] kod ljene privatne lješnice u Zagrebu.

290
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je isto znači potvrdila to,

291
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:53,379
[SPEAKER_00] savjetovala opet da dobro razmislimo,

292
00:13:53,379 --> 00:13:57,419
[SPEAKER_00] da smo svjesni što mi s time preuzivamo u svojom životu.

293
00:13:57,419 --> 00:14:01,200
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad smo se vraćali u autobusu iz Splita

294
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,820
[SPEAKER_02] smo dobili poziv.

295
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,899
[SPEAKER_02] Iz Zagreba za Splite smo dobili poziv

296
00:14:04,899 --> 00:14:06,620
[SPEAKER_02] da man je bio nalaz gotov,

297
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:08,159
[SPEAKER_02] to sa Svetog Duha.

298
00:14:08,159 --> 00:14:11,539
[SPEAKER_02] I doktorica mi je rekla kao nalazvan je gotov,

299
00:14:11,539 --> 00:14:13,159
[SPEAKER_02] nije u redu, ja govorim

300
00:14:13,159 --> 00:14:15,120
[SPEAKER_02] šta nije u redu, o čemu se radi,

301
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,620
[SPEAKER_02] kao ima Downov sindrom,

302
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,919
[SPEAKER_02] ja govorim, to vro kao, ok.

303
00:14:19,919 --> 00:14:23,539
[SPEAKER_02] I ona meni na to odgovara kao

304
00:14:23,539 --> 00:14:26,639
[SPEAKER_02] ja ću vam poslat kao nalaz mail-on,

305
00:14:26,639 --> 00:14:29,519
[SPEAKER_02] pa vidite u Splitsko rodilište to riješiti.

306
00:14:29,519 --> 00:14:33,419
[SPEAKER_02] Ja joj govorim, šta mislite,

307
00:14:33,419 --> 00:14:35,000
[SPEAKER_02] neću ja ništa rješavaka,

308
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,360
[SPEAKER_02] to je naše djete.

309
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,700
[SPEAKER_02] I to se ona toliko zvunila,

310
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:41,259
[SPEAKER_02] toliko je počela zamuckivati,

311
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:43,039
[SPEAKER_02] nije znala še će mi odgovorit.

312
00:14:43,039 --> 00:14:45,539
[SPEAKER_02] Ono ba, ba, ba, da dobro,

313
00:14:45,539 --> 00:14:46,539
[SPEAKER_02] kao, ok,

314
00:14:46,539 --> 00:14:49,600
[SPEAKER_02] posla će ovo nja mail-on nalaz, pa...

315
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ona je aludirala da odeš u bolunci

316
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] da povaciš, jel da?

317
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:52,779
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

318
00:14:52,779 --> 00:14:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znači si cijelo vrijeme

319
00:14:55,039 --> 00:14:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] su doktorji to aludirali i savjetovali,

320
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:59,379
[SPEAKER_00] znači nije uopće bilo razgovor,

321
00:14:59,379 --> 00:15:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] da će on mi...

322
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] Povaciš, jel da?

323
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,240
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

324
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,500
[SPEAKER_00] Da, znači si cijelo vrijeme

325
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:06,100
[SPEAKER_00] su doktorji to aludirali i savjetovali,

326
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,860
[SPEAKER_00] znači nije uopće bilo razgovor,

327
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] da će on mi uopće iš drugim smjerom.

328
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ovaj...

329
00:15:11,179 --> 00:15:12,100
[SPEAKER_00] O svih tih doktora,

330
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] znači jedino jedan liječnik,

331
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,419
[SPEAKER_00] nakladno kad smo morali napraviti

332
00:15:15,419 --> 00:15:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] ultrazug srca,

333
00:15:16,659 --> 00:15:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] znači i kod fetalnog kardiologa,

334
00:15:19,639 --> 00:15:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji jedino u Zagrebu na rebru ima,

335
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,019
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad smo ušli,

336
00:15:24,019 --> 00:15:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] znam, kad sam ušao pogledao sam,

337
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] vidio sam mu na stolu

338
00:15:26,779 --> 00:15:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] glas koncila i sliku majke Tereza,

339
00:15:29,759 --> 00:15:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] ja govim, napokon jedan normalan.

340
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] I tako je i bilo,

341
00:15:34,139 --> 00:15:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] počeo je pregled,

342
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:37,159
[SPEAKER_00] jedno 10-15 minuta,

343
00:15:37,159 --> 00:15:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] doktor šuti,

344
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:38,899
[SPEAKER_00] gleda,

345
00:15:38,899 --> 00:15:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] ja njemu iza leđa,

346
00:15:40,299 --> 00:15:40,740
[SPEAKER_00] gledam nju,

347
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] ona mene zbunja,

348
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,620
[SPEAKER_00] ni šta će sad bit?

349
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:45,419
[SPEAKER_00] Ja on progovorim,

350
00:15:45,419 --> 00:15:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] dobro je sve u redu,

351
00:15:47,179 --> 00:15:49,179
[SPEAKER_00] u čemu je kvaka,

352
00:15:49,179 --> 00:15:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] oko 60% djece sa daunom sindromom

353
00:15:54,559 --> 00:15:57,820
[SPEAKER_00] se rodi sa srčanom manom,

354
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] što manjom, što većom,

355
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] većinom je potreban operativni zahvat

356
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] odmah po rođenju,

357
00:16:04,759 --> 00:16:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne jedan,

358
00:16:05,679 --> 00:16:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] obično bude više,

359
00:16:06,639 --> 00:16:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] automatski činje srce u razvoju,

360
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,379
[SPEAKER_00] nije u redu,

361
00:16:11,379 --> 00:16:13,299
[SPEAKER_00] cijeli organizam se loše razvije.

362
00:16:13,299 --> 00:16:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] Dok je namo sad i ta lješnik,

363
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] ono s čudom gledao,

364
00:16:17,179 --> 00:16:18,080
[SPEAKER_00] gleda nalaz,

365
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači potvrđeno da je daunov sindrom,

366
00:16:20,179 --> 00:16:22,480
[SPEAKER_00] znam samo da je rekao da je srce

367
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:25,379
[SPEAKER_00] dobro ne za djete s daunovim sindromom,

368
00:16:25,379 --> 00:16:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] nego čak i za djete bez poteškoća,

369
00:16:28,279 --> 00:16:29,240
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

370
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] zdravo srce,

371
00:16:30,779 --> 00:16:32,120
[SPEAKER_00] 100%.

372
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] Kako si se ti tada osjećao?

373
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:39,299
[SPEAKER_01] Kako si proživljava to sve?

374
00:16:39,299 --> 00:16:41,120
[SPEAKER_00] Pa olakšanje,

375
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] prvo što napoko ima neko

376
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] s nekim normalnim razgovarat,

377
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:47,399
[SPEAKER_00] jer nakon pregleda on nama rekao,

378
00:16:47,399 --> 00:16:49,580
[SPEAKER_00] a mora reći da se ne bojimo,

379
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:53,399
[SPEAKER_00] da se s djecom s daunovim sindromom može puno toga postići,

380
00:16:53,399 --> 00:16:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se treba raditi puno,

381
00:16:56,000 --> 00:17:01,259
[SPEAKER_00] ali da se to nosi normalno svoju ljepotu i radost.

382
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju, vamu reći ono,

383
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] bilo mu je drago da smo,

384
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] to nam je rekao da mu je drago da smo se odlučili išći do kraja,

385
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] da nismo prekinuli trudnoć.

386
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] A jeste li u tom periodu,

387
00:17:14,559 --> 00:17:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] mislim rodbina naravno,

388
00:17:16,099 --> 00:17:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelji si,

389
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:19,759
[SPEAKER_01] jer vidim da i ovdje neki prijatelji pozdravljaju kumove i tako,

390
00:17:20,339 --> 00:17:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] kako je okolina reagirala,

391
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,579
[SPEAKER_01] jer su znali što se događa,

392
00:17:23,579 --> 00:17:27,500
[SPEAKER_01] jer najčešće nekada je i okolina veliki pritisak.

393
00:17:29,299 --> 00:17:32,619
[SPEAKER_02] Naši stvarno su i roditelji i braća i sestre,

394
00:17:32,619 --> 00:17:35,740
[SPEAKER_02] stvarno najbliža rodbina je bila uz nas od prvoga dana.

395
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:41,960
[SPEAKER_02] Podupirali su na šta god da smo mi odlučili,

396
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:45,960
[SPEAKER_02] stali su iza nas doslovce,

397
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:51,400
[SPEAKER_02] dok ono malo dalji su govorili kao pre mladi ste,

398
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:54,079
[SPEAKER_02] šta vama to treba i tako dalje,

399
00:17:54,079 --> 00:17:56,279
[SPEAKER_02] ali njih nismo slušali.

400
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] A ko vam je onda bio najveća podrška u tom periodu?

401
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:04,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mislim, baš naša je to obitelj,

402
00:18:04,539 --> 00:18:07,180
[SPEAKER_00] i njezina i moja strana,

403
00:18:07,180 --> 00:18:08,319
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno su veke,

404
00:18:08,319 --> 00:18:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] kad je to još bilo na početku,

405
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] što god odlučite,

406
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:12,220
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo uz vas,

407
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] znači i u molitvi i u svemu,

408
00:18:16,039 --> 00:18:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] jer, znači želim,

409
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,339
[SPEAKER_00] krenuti s ovom temom,

410
00:18:20,339 --> 00:18:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] znači malo vjerskom,

411
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,799
[SPEAKER_00] molitva je ovdje učinila jedno veliko čudo.

412
00:18:27,059 --> 00:18:29,099
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, da je neko vidio,

413
00:18:29,099 --> 00:18:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo ko se,

414
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] da je to razumiju malo više u to,

415
00:18:31,579 --> 00:18:38,279
[SPEAKER_00] nalaz, to jest snimku ultrazvuka,

416
00:18:38,279 --> 00:18:39,759
[SPEAKER_00] znači naš Dominik,

417
00:18:39,759 --> 00:18:43,019
[SPEAKER_00] kad je bio veličina otprilike 6 centimetara,

418
00:18:43,019 --> 00:18:45,359
[SPEAKER_00] kad je bio kao djete,

419
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] kao plod,

420
00:18:46,079 --> 00:18:48,980
[SPEAKER_00] znači on je bio imao taj nabor

421
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] i obavijen to tekućinom,

422
00:18:51,099 --> 00:18:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] koji oni nisu uopće znali što je to,

423
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,019
[SPEAKER_00] oni nisu uspili nama,

424
00:18:54,019 --> 00:18:57,839
[SPEAKER_00] to što mi nismo dobili na kraju potvrdu šta je to bilo.

425
00:18:57,839 --> 00:19:03,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo 8 milimetara debljine od glave leđa,

426
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] jedino, mislim, lice i trbuh nije bilo obavijeno.

427
00:19:06,259 --> 00:19:09,500
[SPEAKER_02] i glice, mislim, samo nije bilo.

428
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:14,240
[SPEAKER_00] I to je stvarno bilo bružno za vidjeti u tom omjeru tada,

429
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] znači kada smo imali.

430
00:19:15,279 --> 00:19:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] I normalno priča se raširila,

431
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:23,680
[SPEAKER_00] znači unutar naše obitelji, rodbine, prijatelja,

432
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] i ta molitva je krenula,

433
00:19:27,099 --> 00:19:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] širila se sve više,

434
00:19:29,039 --> 00:19:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] i jednostavno čudo se počelo događati.

435
00:19:35,599 --> 00:19:40,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, prvo, Betoviš želi napomenuti jednu stvar,

436
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači u ovim tako teškim trenucima,

437
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:48,759
[SPEAKER_00] teško je pokazati da će tako vjeru,

438
00:19:48,759 --> 00:19:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] onu konkretnu, lako je govoriti,

439
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:53,079
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine, ja vjerujem,

440
00:19:53,079 --> 00:19:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad zagusti, e onda krene,

441
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi kad smo saznali ovo,

442
00:19:58,019 --> 00:20:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo pri par dana,

443
00:20:00,519 --> 00:20:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] emocije divljaju od plakanja,

444
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] suza suza ugorni, ti više ne znaš kako razmišljati,

445
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:10,299
[SPEAKER_00] pa Bože, zašto?

446
00:20:10,299 --> 00:20:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, stvarno ti misliš da to mogu,

447
00:20:12,579 --> 00:20:14,579
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, zašto mi, ono,

448
00:20:14,579 --> 00:20:17,660
[SPEAKER_00] ono, djelostavno ne možeš to pojmiti,

449
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] i bio je tada, znači, ono Božečno,

450
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,279
[SPEAKER_00] prvo Božečno vrijeme, advent,

451
00:20:23,279 --> 00:20:25,339
[SPEAKER_00] i znam da sam otišao ovdje,

452
00:20:25,339 --> 00:20:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] pošto živimo u Solinu,

453
00:20:26,660 --> 00:20:28,099
[SPEAKER_00] radimo u Splitu, živimo u Solinu,

454
00:20:28,099 --> 00:20:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] u crku Odeh,

455
00:20:30,819 --> 00:20:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] i ovdje sam otišao na Misu Zornicu,

456
00:20:32,099 --> 00:20:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] ali, eto, iz nekog razloga,

457
00:20:35,559 --> 00:20:37,519
[SPEAKER_00] možda i to bila providnost,

458
00:20:37,519 --> 00:20:38,799
[SPEAKER_00] u puno slučajeva,

459
00:20:38,799 --> 00:20:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] evo, kaj je ovaj naš susret,

460
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] oprije mjesec,

461
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] danas se nismo uopće ni znali,

462
00:20:42,579 --> 00:20:43,900
[SPEAKER_00] ni poznavali,

463
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] evo, već smo odeo u live-u s vama,

464
00:20:46,519 --> 00:20:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] otišao sam na tu zornicu,

465
00:20:48,039 --> 00:20:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] to je zornic,

466
00:20:48,579 --> 00:20:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] već bila gotova,

467
00:20:49,279 --> 00:20:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam pogriješao kaj je termin,

468
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] i sa u Solinu ima,

469
00:20:53,019 --> 00:20:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači, nakon ulaznih vrata,

470
00:20:54,579 --> 00:20:55,740
[SPEAKER_00] par metara prostora,

471
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] nas je jedna stakljena vrata,

472
00:20:57,039 --> 00:21:00,200
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo nikoga tada,

473
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,140
[SPEAKER_00] bilo možda šesti po sedam ujutro,

474
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] znam da sam tu kleknio,

475
00:21:03,859 --> 00:21:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] i prvi put,

476
00:21:04,759 --> 00:21:06,099
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno ono iskreno,

477
00:21:06,099 --> 00:21:07,799
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu iznio sve,

478
00:21:07,799 --> 00:21:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] kod da pričam s nabojim prijateljem,

479
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:10,680
[SPEAKER_00] sa bratom,

480
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] i jednostavno ja sam reklamo,

481
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] Bože,

482
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,019
[SPEAKER_00] ja vjerujem,

483
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,319
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek sve vjerujem da je s nekim razlogom,

484
00:21:17,319 --> 00:21:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ne studbina,

485
00:21:19,039 --> 00:21:19,799
[SPEAKER_00] nego kao ste vi rekli,

486
00:21:19,799 --> 00:21:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] prst Boži,

487
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] znači, da je sve s nekim razlogom,

488
00:21:23,660 --> 00:21:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam rekao,

489
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, dobro,

490
00:21:25,079 --> 00:21:26,220
[SPEAKER_00] ti imaš neki plan,

491
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja,

492
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] Sanja,

493
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] mi to ne možemo,

494
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:29,819
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

495
00:21:29,819 --> 00:21:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] mi sa svojim naporom,

496
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,299
[SPEAKER_00] svojom snagom,

497
00:21:32,299 --> 00:21:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] mi to ne možemo napraviti,

498
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:33,680
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

499
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] trebaš nam ti,

500
00:21:35,019 --> 00:21:36,299
[SPEAKER_00] tvoja pomoć,

501
00:21:36,299 --> 00:21:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] tvoje vosto,

502
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] ti gospodine,

503
00:21:38,119 --> 00:21:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] preuzmi ti vodi,

504
00:21:39,059 --> 00:21:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] i tu sam prvo neko vrijeme,

505
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

506
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] sve što mi je bilo na duši,

507
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:46,680
[SPEAKER_00] na srcu sam rekao gospodinu

508
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] i već,

509
00:21:48,279 --> 00:21:48,660
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

510
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] neki mir,

511
00:21:49,339 --> 00:21:50,319
[SPEAKER_00] osjetio da će,

512
00:21:50,319 --> 00:21:51,740
[SPEAKER_00] da će bit,

513
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] bit sve u redu,

514
00:21:53,119 --> 00:21:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] a zašto,

515
00:21:55,279 --> 00:21:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] imamo reć,

516
00:21:55,819 --> 00:21:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] oprosti što se ubacujem,

517
00:21:58,019 --> 00:21:59,720
[SPEAKER_01] a mislim da takih situacija,

518
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] nekako teže muškarcima,

519
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] slomice,

520
00:22:02,119 --> 00:22:04,740
[SPEAKER_01] majke dobio odmah taj maječinski,

521
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] neki osjećaj,

522
00:22:05,519 --> 00:22:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] instikt maječinstva,

523
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,220
[SPEAKER_01] i one puno ne kalkuliraju,

524
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:09,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali mislim da je nekako muškarcima,

525
00:22:09,779 --> 00:22:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] ono što sad pričaš,

526
00:22:11,599 --> 00:22:12,400
[SPEAKER_01] da si proživljava,

527
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer na početku je bilo straha za budućnost,

528
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] znači što, kako,

529
00:22:24,819 --> 00:22:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] toliko od toga ti prođe kroz glavu,

530
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] šta će bit s tim djetetom,

531
00:22:28,859 --> 00:22:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] odmah kakvi će život imati,

532
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] šta kad nas ne bude jednog dana,

533
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] o čemu li li će imati više djece iza njega,

534
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] toliko tih pitanja je bilo,

535
00:22:38,119 --> 00:22:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali,

536
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] evo, volio bi istaknuti,

537
00:22:41,619 --> 00:22:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] kao ste vi isto sa drugim gostima znali,

538
00:22:44,559 --> 00:22:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] ono, neko štivo preporučiti,

539
00:22:46,579 --> 00:22:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] znači knjiga koja je meni promijenila život,

540
00:22:49,339 --> 00:22:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] znači to je

541
00:22:51,039 --> 00:22:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] dnevnik Svete Faustine Kovalske,

542
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] eto preporučan,

543
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,740
[SPEAKER_00] ako ko ima priliku je nabaviti,

544
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:58,759
[SPEAKER_00] možda čak u ovom periodu,

545
00:22:58,759 --> 00:23:00,160
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo svi doma imate vremena,

546
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] je da malo ima više stranica,

547
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] skoro 500 stranica,

548
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:04,759
[SPEAKER_00] gdje, znači,

549
00:23:04,759 --> 00:23:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] Isus Svete Faustini

550
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] pokazuje,

551
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:10,079
[SPEAKER_00] znači, smisao patnje,

552
00:23:10,759 --> 00:23:13,440
[SPEAKER_00] smisao poteškoće u životu

553
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:16,759
[SPEAKER_00] i želim naglasiti,

554
00:23:16,759 --> 00:23:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao što se i vi u jednoj emisiji,

555
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

556
00:23:19,220 --> 00:23:20,680
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ne kažnjava,

557
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:23,720
[SPEAKER_00] Bog preko patnje,

558
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] preko nekog križa,

559
00:23:26,119 --> 00:23:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] jedino spašava,

560
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili nas,

561
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] ili nekoga drugoga.

562
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] Sveta Faustina je umrla,

563
00:23:31,779 --> 00:23:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] mlada u 33. godini,

564
00:23:33,759 --> 00:23:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] sa toliko,

565
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:37,839
[SPEAKER_00] bolesti na svom tijelu,

566
00:23:37,839 --> 00:23:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] koja je sve

567
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] prihvatila svojevoljno

568
00:23:41,819 --> 00:23:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] za spas drugih,

569
00:23:43,759 --> 00:23:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo duša u čistilištu.

570
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:47,160
[SPEAKER_00] I tada sam,

571
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,740
[SPEAKER_00] od kad sam pročitao ovu knjigu,

572
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:49,259
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam

573
00:23:49,259 --> 00:23:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] počeo

574
00:23:50,079 --> 00:23:52,079
[SPEAKER_00] i prihvatio da u svom životu

575
00:23:52,079 --> 00:23:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] da je znači sve,

576
00:23:52,980 --> 00:23:53,779
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno sve

577
00:23:53,779 --> 00:23:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] s nekim razlogom,

578
00:23:54,839 --> 00:23:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] bit će biljivo,

579
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:57,759
[SPEAKER_00] ili Lizu,

580
00:23:57,759 --> 00:23:58,720
[SPEAKER_00] ili jednoga dana,

581
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,579
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek ćeš shvatiti

582
00:23:59,579 --> 00:24:00,700
[SPEAKER_00] kad imaš neki križ,

583
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je to bilo,

584
00:24:02,119 --> 00:24:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] zašto te godi možda pripremao,

585
00:24:03,539 --> 00:24:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] za možda još nešto veće,

586
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] tu ljepotu ćeš vidjeti,

587
00:24:07,079 --> 00:24:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] kad tad srpljenja treba imati.

588
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] I znao sam,

589
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

590
00:24:11,579 --> 00:24:13,160
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog ima neki plan.

591
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Samo treba onda

592
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] znati živjeti,

593
00:24:16,579 --> 00:24:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] ono što svaki dan molimo,

594
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,700
[SPEAKER_00] budi volja tvoja,

595
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] da ne bude samo puko izgovaranje,

596
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:24,660
[SPEAKER_00] nego da mi stvarno u srcu to

597
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] priznamo i da znamo,

598
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,299
[SPEAKER_00] gospodine,

599
00:24:29,299 --> 00:24:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] evo sad je neki problem,

600
00:24:30,539 --> 00:24:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] ali ti znaš zašto ti si to planirao,

601
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] ti vodi

602
00:24:34,519 --> 00:24:36,420
[SPEAKER_00] i neka se ispuni tvoja volja.

603
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je, znači,

604
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] mene promijenilo

605
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:40,640
[SPEAKER_00] i da nije bilo toga,

606
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno bi teško

607
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,799
[SPEAKER_00] i ko zna kako prihvati ovaj križ,

608
00:24:43,799 --> 00:24:45,339
[SPEAKER_00] ali, znači,

609
00:24:45,339 --> 00:24:47,680
[SPEAKER_00] providnost Božja je bila da,

610
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] da Bogu hvala,

611
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] promijeni svoje mišljenje,

612
00:24:51,819 --> 00:24:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] dovolja.

613
00:24:52,619 --> 00:24:54,480
[SPEAKER_01] Sad nije jasno

614
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,299
[SPEAKER_01] zašto smo se ja ti brzo povezali

615
00:24:56,299 --> 00:24:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] sa vama,

616
00:24:58,319 --> 00:24:59,700
[SPEAKER_01] jer vidiš Milosavnog tu,

617
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

618
00:25:00,559 --> 00:25:01,859
[SPEAKER_01] on i Paustina,

619
00:25:01,859 --> 00:25:03,180
[SPEAKER_01] očigledno imaju prste

620
00:25:03,180 --> 00:25:04,200
[SPEAKER_01] i kod mene i kod vas.

621
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] Drago me da si jel

622
00:25:06,759 --> 00:25:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] istaknu Dnevnih sestre Paustine,

623
00:25:08,559 --> 00:25:09,240
[SPEAKER_01] neki da opite

624
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] koja je to knjiga,

625
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:11,660
[SPEAKER_01] zove se Dnevnih sestre Paustine

626
00:25:11,660 --> 00:25:12,839
[SPEAKER_01] i slobodno je,

627
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] čitajte ljudi,

628
00:25:13,579 --> 00:25:15,400
[SPEAKER_01] nemojte čitati u komadu,

629
00:25:15,759 --> 00:25:16,200
[SPEAKER_01] dovoljno,

630
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,160
[SPEAKER_01] jedna stranica,

631
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:18,200
[SPEAKER_01] imate što razmišljati.

632
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:21,259
[SPEAKER_01] Želiš ti nešto reći,

633
00:25:21,259 --> 00:25:23,140
[SPEAKER_00] mama?

634
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:24,640
[SPEAKER_00] I ovaj,

635
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,359
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

636
00:25:25,359 --> 00:25:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] naš put,

637
00:25:26,099 --> 00:25:26,339
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

638
00:25:26,339 --> 00:25:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] za odlazak,

639
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

640
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] nakon,

641
00:25:30,579 --> 00:25:31,240
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

642
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] išao je taj neki period

643
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] prihvaćanja toga,

644
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] to je kad smo se mi pomirili

645
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:36,559
[SPEAKER_00] sa svim,

646
00:25:36,559 --> 00:25:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] i zatim smo otišli,

647
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:38,700
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

648
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:39,140
[SPEAKER_00] opet,

649
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,799
[SPEAKER_00] ja volim to reći,

650
00:25:40,859 --> 00:25:41,799
[SPEAKER_00] providnost Božja,

651
00:25:41,799 --> 00:25:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] naš prijatelj,

652
00:25:44,579 --> 00:25:45,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nikola Šakić,

653
00:25:45,660 --> 00:25:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji je,

654
00:25:46,039 --> 00:25:46,200
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

655
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] vogu hvala,

656
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:48,299
[SPEAKER_00] još za koji mjeseć,

657
00:25:48,299 --> 00:25:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] je mladomisnik,

658
00:25:49,619 --> 00:25:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] bivši kolega,

659
00:25:51,579 --> 00:25:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

660
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] bili smo zajedno na istom brodu

661
00:25:53,319 --> 00:25:54,140
[SPEAKER_00] u Mornarici,

662
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] gdje radim,

663
00:25:55,359 --> 00:25:57,200
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

664
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] on je,

665
00:25:57,980 --> 00:25:58,839
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam ja počeo

666
00:25:58,839 --> 00:25:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] radit dvih desete,

667
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,119
[SPEAKER_00] na tom brodu,

668
00:26:02,119 --> 00:26:03,700
[SPEAKER_00] on je tada još bio vojnik,

669
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] topnik,

670
00:26:04,599 --> 00:26:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] pa se volimo zezati,

671
00:26:06,059 --> 00:26:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] da je njegov put bio

672
00:26:07,019 --> 00:26:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] od topa do popa,

673
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] i evo još za koji mjeseć će biti svečenik,

674
00:26:11,759 --> 00:26:13,180
[SPEAKER_00] i on je,

675
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

676
00:26:13,519 --> 00:26:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] bila je duhovna obnova

677
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] u župi Katuni,

678
00:26:17,039 --> 00:26:17,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kreševo,

679
00:26:17,660 --> 00:26:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] to je kod Don Mija Grozdanića,

680
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] za njega ste čuli ovih dana po medijima,

681
00:26:22,599 --> 00:26:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad je bio sa presvetim po selu,

682
00:26:25,539 --> 00:26:26,460
[SPEAKER_00] išao i danas,

683
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] kako je svim župljanima dostavio,

684
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

685
00:26:29,180 --> 00:26:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] palmine, grančice,

686
00:26:30,900 --> 00:26:31,440
[SPEAKER_00] križ,

687
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] vodu,

688
00:26:31,799 --> 00:26:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] sol i sve što treba,

689
00:26:33,359 --> 00:26:35,640
[SPEAKER_00] i, znači,

690
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] opet mi smo dobili poziv,

691
00:26:37,019 --> 00:26:38,299
[SPEAKER_00] kao poziv u Međugorje,

692
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:41,079
[SPEAKER_00] tako i poziv za tu duhovnu obnovu,

693
00:26:41,079 --> 00:26:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] trodnevnicu,

694
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:43,359
[SPEAKER_00] opet preko nekoga,

695
00:26:43,359 --> 00:26:43,759
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

696
00:26:43,759 --> 00:26:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je to sve planirao i za nas,

697
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] i, znači,

698
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] šti moleć,

699
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] ja sve,

700
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] i bili smo,

701
00:26:55,359 --> 00:26:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

702
00:26:55,579 --> 00:26:56,640
[SPEAKER_00] na to duhovno obnovi,

703
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,619
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju,

704
00:26:57,619 --> 00:26:59,299
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo,

705
00:26:59,299 --> 00:27:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] polaganje ruku,

706
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,640
[SPEAKER_00] i tada je,

707
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

708
00:27:02,980 --> 00:27:03,740
[SPEAKER_00] u tom trenu,

709
00:27:03,740 --> 00:27:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad je svećenik,

710
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] položio ruke na nas,

711
00:27:07,819 --> 00:27:10,119
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo se držali za ruke,

712
00:27:10,119 --> 00:27:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam zatvorio oči i osjetio,

713
00:27:12,519 --> 00:27:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

714
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] da me duh sveti preuzima,

715
00:27:15,599 --> 00:27:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] i mi na kraju,

716
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam,

717
00:27:17,779 --> 00:27:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

718
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] na podu otvorio oči,

719
00:27:20,180 --> 00:27:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] vidim,

720
00:27:20,579 --> 00:27:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] leži ona kraj mene,

721
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje se držimo za ruke,

722
00:27:23,339 --> 00:27:24,940
[SPEAKER_00] nas su nam ljudi rekli,

723
00:27:24,940 --> 00:27:25,859
[SPEAKER_00] da smo mi isto vremeno,

724
00:27:25,859 --> 00:27:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] pođivali u duhu,

725
00:27:27,619 --> 00:27:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] i kad smo se ustali,

726
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,700
[SPEAKER_00] svećenik nas je zagrljio,

727
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] blagoslovio,

728
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,839
[SPEAKER_00] i nevjerojatno,

729
00:27:34,839 --> 00:27:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] kakav smo mi mir osjetili,

730
00:27:36,859 --> 00:27:38,160
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

731
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,779
[SPEAKER_00] ušli smo kao jedne osobe u tu crkvu,

732
00:27:40,779 --> 00:27:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] izašli kao totalno promijenjene,

733
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] ispunjeni tolikim mirom,

734
00:27:45,759 --> 00:27:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] da će sve biti u redu,

735
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] da je to jednostavno,

736
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] bi bilo neopisivo,

737
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] i nakon toga,

738
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

739
00:27:54,779 --> 00:27:55,799
[SPEAKER_00] bi opet pregled,

740
00:27:55,799 --> 00:27:57,359
[SPEAKER_02] nakon toga je bio pregled,

741
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:58,480
[SPEAKER_02] i ona sva tekućina,

742
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,880
[SPEAKER_02] koja je bila oko Dominika,

743
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,980
[SPEAKER_02] se povukla.

744
00:28:00,980 --> 00:28:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jednostavno je sve nestalo.

745
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] A opet,

746
00:28:05,599 --> 00:28:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] dašto šelim puno toga naglasiti,

747
00:28:07,819 --> 00:28:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer puno roditelja,

748
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] da li će tako ne imalo milost,

749
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] možda nekad i bolje,

750
00:28:15,059 --> 00:28:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako bi reagirali,

751
00:28:16,599 --> 00:28:20,759
[SPEAKER_00] ali puno roditelja sazna za djecu,

752
00:28:20,759 --> 00:28:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači po porodu,

753
00:28:22,059 --> 00:28:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] da imaju Downo sindrom.

754
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] I onda tu bude veliko razočaranje.

755
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,240
[SPEAKER_00] Šok.

756
00:28:27,259 --> 00:28:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] šok i sve.

757
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo imali,

758
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,160
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

759
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:32,240
[SPEAKER_00] tu sreću da smo uvidjeli

760
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,400
[SPEAKER_00] da nešto nije u redu.

761
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] Imali smo vremena pripremi se,

762
00:28:35,759 --> 00:28:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] jedno s drugim,

763
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,759
[SPEAKER_00] sa gospodinom.

764
00:28:38,759 --> 00:28:41,240
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je Bog napravio to čudo,

765
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je,

766
00:28:41,579 --> 00:28:42,019
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

767
00:28:42,019 --> 00:28:45,160
[SPEAKER_00] po rukama svećenika,

768
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] udjelio nama mir,

769
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] i mi vjerujemo,

770
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:51,640
[SPEAKER_00] uklonio sve to što je bilo,

771
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] ugrožavalo njegov život.

772
00:28:53,559 --> 00:28:55,680
[SPEAKER_00] Znali smo,

773
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

774
00:28:56,039 --> 00:28:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] iskreno nismo vjerali da će

775
00:28:57,779 --> 00:29:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] sindrom kao sindrom cijeli nestati,

776
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali s obzirom,

777
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

778
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,799
[SPEAKER_00] sad smo više u toj temi,

779
00:29:03,799 --> 00:29:05,619
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ljudi,

780
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

781
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] ima djecu sa velikim,

782
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,240
[SPEAKER_00] zdravstvenim po teškovačama,

783
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] govorimo o djeci sa Down-ovim sindromom.

784
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,660
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

785
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] naš Dominik nema ni srčanu grešku,

786
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:16,619
[SPEAKER_00] nikakvu drugu popratnu,

787
00:29:16,619 --> 00:29:17,859
[SPEAKER_00] rečano maliju,

788
00:29:17,859 --> 00:29:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] neko zdravstveno stanje,

789
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] koje ga teže,

790
00:29:22,339 --> 00:29:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] koje ga kođi tu život.

791
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] I smatram da je to isto veliko čudo,

792
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] znamenje i blagoslov koji smo dobili,

793
00:29:29,619 --> 00:29:30,319
[SPEAKER_00] kada smo svano

794
00:29:30,319 --> 00:29:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] gospodinu rekli da,

795
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] i prihvatili to što nam je dao.

796
00:29:35,019 --> 00:29:35,859
[SPEAKER_00] Jer je bitno,

797
00:29:35,859 --> 00:29:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] bitno gospodinu dati prostora da on djeluje.

798
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ako smo mi zatvoreni,

799
00:29:40,339 --> 00:29:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] on nama daje tu slobodu.

800
00:29:42,339 --> 00:29:44,119
[SPEAKER_00] Češ ti ići ljevo, desno,

801
00:29:44,119 --> 00:29:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] radi što ga hoćeš.

802
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:49,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali opet kada mi se uvidimo gdje smo,

803
00:29:49,259 --> 00:29:50,380
[SPEAKER_00] kada damo tu ruku,

804
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno čuda se događaju,

805
00:29:52,940 --> 00:29:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] na slavu njegovu,

806
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] a i da drugi vide i znamo zašto.

807
00:29:58,539 --> 00:30:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] Samo ni nastavite pričati,

808
00:30:03,319 --> 00:30:05,700
[SPEAKER_01] meni je doliko teško i pitanja vam uopće postavljati.

809
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:06,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

810
00:30:06,259 --> 00:30:11,539
[SPEAKER_02] Uvidjela sam odaj jedno pitanje u vezi poroda.

811
00:30:11,539 --> 00:30:14,839
[SPEAKER_02] Porod kao porod je bio odličan,

812
00:30:14,839 --> 00:30:16,579
[SPEAKER_02] osoblje super.

813
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] čak čin se rodio Dominik,

814
00:30:20,559 --> 00:30:24,420
[SPEAKER_02] počeo je mijenjati ljude oko sebe.

815
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:27,200
[SPEAKER_02] Jer oni kad su vidjeli,

816
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,940
[SPEAKER_02] kako smo mi njega zagrljeli,

817
00:30:28,940 --> 00:30:31,019
[SPEAKER_02] kako smo mi njega počeli ljubiti,

818
00:30:31,019 --> 00:30:33,539
[SPEAKER_02] sriću u našim očima,

819
00:30:33,539 --> 00:30:36,799
[SPEAKER_02] jednostavno su se ljudi okrenili.

820
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:40,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da, nažalost su navikli veće na suze,

821
00:30:40,299 --> 00:30:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] kod poroda djeca sa Downom sindromom,

822
00:30:42,299 --> 00:30:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] pa što se sjeća glavna sestra, babica,

823
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što se djete opralo i sve ono što treba po samom rođenju.

824
00:30:51,180 --> 00:30:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nam ga je ponovno došla pokazati,

825
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:55,400
[SPEAKER_00] znam da je bilo ono upitnik njoj nad glavom,

826
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] kao vi znate da djeti ima Downom sindromom.

827
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] Mi ono, znamo, ono, svi veseli, smijemo se.

828
00:31:01,279 --> 00:31:04,359
[SPEAKER_00] I ono je bilo malo iznenađenje.

829
00:31:04,359 --> 00:31:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno njima je bilo iznenađenje pozitivno

830
00:31:06,759 --> 00:31:10,819
[SPEAKER_00] i tako da, eto, od samog trenutka rođenja

831
00:31:10,819 --> 00:31:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] je počeo mijenjati i svijest ljudi oko njih, za njih.

832
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:18,519
[SPEAKER_01] O kon sad ima godina?

833
00:31:19,579 --> 00:31:21,420
[SPEAKER_02] Sada će tri u šesti mjesec.

834
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] A vidi se ga na potkama, na potkama je presladak.

835
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:29,200
[SPEAKER_00] Je, stvarno super napreduje.

836
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, potom sad uz brata njih dvoje zajedno rastu, napreduju.

837
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan drugom je oslavnac.

838
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer djeca sa Downom sindromom,

839
00:31:40,220 --> 00:31:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] mi nekad mislimo da su oni, imamo reć,

840
00:31:43,279 --> 00:31:45,259
[SPEAKER_00] zakinuti za nešto,

841
00:31:45,259 --> 00:31:47,700
[SPEAKER_00] a možda smo u stvari mi,

842
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] tako reć, normalni, zdravi ljudi,

843
00:31:51,559 --> 00:31:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] ograničeni, jer

844
00:31:53,279 --> 00:31:56,319
[SPEAKER_00] u njih je ljubav iskrena,

845
00:31:56,319 --> 00:31:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] u njih je emocija, ona prava,

846
00:31:58,220 --> 00:32:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] nema laganja, nema

847
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] pretvaranja, s njih u njih znate

848
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] na čemu ste.

849
00:32:02,980 --> 00:32:05,359
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da smatram da je to

850
00:32:05,359 --> 00:32:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] najnije blagoslov nama,

851
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] jer, evo ja kao

852
00:32:10,019 --> 00:32:11,960
[SPEAKER_00] momaka sa jednog razmišlja,

853
00:32:12,039 --> 00:32:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] ono, jednog dana imat ću,

854
00:32:13,519 --> 00:32:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] ako Bog da, ženu, djecu,

855
00:32:15,279 --> 00:32:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad bi nekad vidio neke roditelje

856
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] sa djecom s poteškoćama,

857
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:21,799
[SPEAKER_00] znao bi reć, ono,

858
00:32:21,799 --> 00:32:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] ajme Bože, ja to nikada ne mogu,

859
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,660
[SPEAKER_00] a koji što u životu nema mi to dat.

860
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:26,380
[SPEAKER_00] I Bog je baš to,

861
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:29,839
[SPEAKER_00] reka, ako misliš da je to baš ono što ne možeš,

862
00:32:29,839 --> 00:32:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] da je to veće i od mene,

863
00:32:32,299 --> 00:32:33,160
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju, eto,

864
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] promijenilo je nas sigurno kao dvojka osobe,

865
00:32:36,460 --> 00:32:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] promijenilo je našu obitelj,

866
00:32:38,519 --> 00:32:39,299
[SPEAKER_00] mijenja ljude,

867
00:32:39,299 --> 00:32:41,359
[SPEAKER_00] baš, eto, ono,

868
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] zarazan, da rečem tako,

869
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,720
[SPEAKER_00] svojom vedrinom, svojim veseljem,

870
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] tako da, vjerujem da će cilj život

871
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,599
[SPEAKER_00] mijenjati ljude oko sebe

872
00:32:50,599 --> 00:32:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] i biti veliki osnovanac

873
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,559
[SPEAKER_00] i on i svom bratu,

874
00:32:54,559 --> 00:32:55,720
[SPEAKER_00] a pogotovo brat njemu,

875
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] tako da,

876
00:32:57,359 --> 00:33:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] bit će to jedna lijepa priča njihova.

877
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] i želio bih napomenuti,

878
00:33:03,779 --> 00:33:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] znači, patera Iliju,

879
00:33:05,039 --> 00:33:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] imali smo velikog,

880
00:33:08,039 --> 00:33:09,019
[SPEAKER_00] većem tako,

881
00:33:09,019 --> 00:33:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] pomoć od,

882
00:33:11,380 --> 00:33:13,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači, pater Ilija Grgić,

883
00:33:13,059 --> 00:33:14,640
[SPEAKER_00] voditelj reda,

884
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] misjonara Krvi Kristove,

885
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,640
[SPEAKER_00] tu u Zagrebu,

886
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] on je bio s nama posebno umoliti,

887
00:33:20,859 --> 00:33:21,720
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

888
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] prije ono što smo saznali,

889
00:33:23,119 --> 00:33:23,940
[SPEAKER_02] početka, da,

890
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] prije ono što smo saznali da imamo problem,

891
00:33:25,579 --> 00:33:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] zatim,

892
00:33:27,119 --> 00:33:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što smo saznali,

893
00:33:29,039 --> 00:33:31,759
[SPEAKER_00] dva navrata smo se ibaš i vidjeli,

894
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] kad je on bio u Splitu,

895
00:33:33,319 --> 00:33:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] pa je u crkvi molio nad nama za nas,

896
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,359
[SPEAKER_00] i jedan put u Zagrebu,

897
00:33:37,359 --> 00:33:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] on je isto znači,

898
00:33:38,819 --> 00:33:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] a to je ono što vi s većenici,

899
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,599
[SPEAKER_00] radite,

900
00:33:42,599 --> 00:33:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] toliki,

901
00:33:43,119 --> 00:33:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] osmijeh, on mir,

902
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] on nam uvijek govore,

903
00:33:46,299 --> 00:33:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] bit će sve u redu,

904
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] ne brinite,

905
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno,

906
00:33:49,400 --> 00:33:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] i onda imamo isto jednu anegdotu za,

907
00:33:51,079 --> 00:33:54,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako je Dominik dobio u stvari ime,

908
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,660
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi smo cijeli život to sve,

909
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] od kad smo zajedno,

910
00:33:57,579 --> 00:33:58,079
[SPEAKER_00] od kad smo,

911
00:33:58,079 --> 00:34:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam opoznao njene roditelje,

912
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:01,660
[SPEAKER_00] pa smo mogli ih zajedno namjesu,

913
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:05,660
[SPEAKER_00] išli i dan danas u crkvu Svetog Dominika,

914
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:07,039
[SPEAKER_00] u Splitu na pazaru,

915
00:34:07,619 --> 00:34:10,400
[SPEAKER_00] a oženili smo se na blagdan Svete Ane,

916
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] koja je zaštitnica obitelji.

917
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:14,460
[SPEAKER_02] Isto u crkvu Svetog Dominika.

918
00:34:14,460 --> 00:34:17,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Dominik Sveta Ana je bilo,

919
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] i ti si izrazila želju da,

920
00:34:20,019 --> 00:34:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] ako bude dječak,

921
00:34:22,260 --> 00:34:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] da bude Dominik,

922
00:34:23,199 --> 00:34:25,420
[SPEAKER_00] a ako bude curica,

923
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:28,139
[SPEAKER_00] prvo od dva prijedloga koje smo imali,

924
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] je bilo da bude Ana,

925
00:34:30,039 --> 00:34:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] i jednom priliku,

926
00:34:32,460 --> 00:34:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači nakon te molitve,

927
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] ponovo, znači nama Pater Ilija,

928
00:34:36,039 --> 00:34:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] sa smiješkom, ne brinite,

929
00:34:37,539 --> 00:34:38,440
[SPEAKER_00] biće sve u redu,

930
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] molite se Svetoj Ani i Svetom Dominiku.

931
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] On nije znao,

932
00:34:42,579 --> 00:34:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ne znao da idemo na mislu,

933
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] i da smo se ženili na Svetu Anu,

934
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] i da je to,

935
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,179
[SPEAKER_00] znači ta dva imena,

936
00:34:48,179 --> 00:34:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] izvojim,

937
00:34:48,539 --> 00:34:50,800
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo se samo pogledali,

938
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] i rekli to je to,

939
00:34:51,599 --> 00:34:52,639
[SPEAKER_00] biće Dominik.

940
00:34:52,639 --> 00:34:55,960
[SPEAKER_01] Krasno, krasno.

941
00:34:55,960 --> 00:35:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno, stvarno vam se divim,

942
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,920
[SPEAKER_01] ja svaku večer,

943
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] znači, da sam nasmijen,

944
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,219
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje postavljam pitanja sve,

945
00:35:04,219 --> 00:35:05,699
[SPEAKER_01] ali već ja sam biste eksternik,

946
00:35:05,780 --> 00:35:06,659
[SPEAKER_01] medla stoji u grlu,

947
00:35:06,659 --> 00:35:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] slušajući vas,

948
00:35:07,519 --> 00:35:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] i znači vam Bogu,

949
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] jer on je stvarno,

950
00:35:10,519 --> 00:35:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] bezlažen neki,

951
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] jer ja često i dobijam poruke,

952
00:35:14,960 --> 00:35:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi koji ne mogu ostati trudni.

953
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] Neki dan sam imao jedan par,

954
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,360
[SPEAKER_01] koji su uletli onako,

955
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] znači,

956
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] pražit će samo mišljenje,

957
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo, oni su ni oženjeni,

958
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] cura je ostalo slučajno trudna,

959
00:35:26,579 --> 00:35:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] i ona želi roditi,

960
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:30,480
[SPEAKER_01] da čovjek praži sva prava.

961
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

962
00:35:31,059 --> 00:35:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su moja prava,

963
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] to ako ja ne želim.

964
00:35:32,679 --> 00:35:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

965
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] koliko negativnih priča slušam o tome,

966
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] i kad slučam vašu ljubavi,

967
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] skupam se da ste ovo prihvatili,

968
00:35:40,260 --> 00:35:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] ja,

969
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:43,880
[SPEAKER_01] samo da vam Bogu zakvaljim,

970
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:44,559
[SPEAKER_01] nasvima vama.

971
00:35:44,559 --> 00:35:46,719
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vama.

972
00:35:46,719 --> 00:35:49,880
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da mladi ovo slušaju i pamte,

973
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] a možda sam posebno večas osvjetljiv,

974
00:35:52,619 --> 00:35:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] možda to ne znaju mnogi,

975
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja treba ubiti abortirati,

976
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] znaš.

977
00:35:55,659 --> 00:36:00,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam deveto djete obitelj,

978
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] i normalno da u moj mjestu,

979
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] odakle ja dolazim,

980
00:36:04,559 --> 00:36:05,679
[SPEAKER_01] imate devetero djece,

981
00:36:05,679 --> 00:36:06,840
[SPEAKER_01] to već bilo previše,

982
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] ja da su moje mami svi savjetovali,

983
00:36:09,579 --> 00:36:10,639
[SPEAKER_01] šta će ti deveto djete,

984
00:36:10,639 --> 00:36:11,480
[SPEAKER_01] pobaci ga,

985
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:13,679
[SPEAKER_01] čak i bliža rodbina,

986
00:36:13,679 --> 00:36:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

987
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je tu uvijek prepričavala djete,

988
00:36:17,059 --> 00:36:18,780
[SPEAKER_01] drago, ja sam samo vjerovala u Boga,

989
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] i vjerovala sam ako sam uspjela odhraniti,

990
00:36:21,579 --> 00:36:23,820
[SPEAKER_01] osmjero djece odhraniti i tebe.

991
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:28,019
[SPEAKER_01] I moja mama je bila sama doma,

992
00:36:28,019 --> 00:36:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] kad je dobila trudove,

993
00:36:30,239 --> 00:36:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] znači to je bilo na selu,

994
00:36:31,679 --> 00:36:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] u selu je tada umrla jedna žena,

995
00:36:33,699 --> 00:36:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] svi su otčina s provod,

996
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,519
[SPEAKER_01] tata je bio na poslu,

997
00:36:36,519 --> 00:36:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] starija djeca su bila u školi,

998
00:36:38,579 --> 00:36:40,639
[SPEAKER_01] i tada nije bilo telefona i ostalo ga.

999
00:36:40,639 --> 00:36:42,300
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kaže ona,

1000
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam dobila trudove,

1001
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] i morala sam izabrat,

1002
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] moram te roditi,

1003
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] a sama sam.

1004
00:36:47,179 --> 00:36:49,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, osmjero djete sam rodila u bolnice,

1005
00:36:49,940 --> 00:36:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali nijedno nisam rodila kod kuće,

1006
00:36:52,039 --> 00:36:54,599
[SPEAKER_01] i nijedno djeto nisam morala sama pupak prevezati.

1007
00:36:54,599 --> 00:36:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ona je uvijek isticela kako je o Bogu isto pomaguo sam.

1008
00:36:58,019 --> 00:36:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ona kaže,

1009
00:36:58,599 --> 00:37:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] djete, ja sam u jednu ruku uzela krunicu,

1010
00:37:00,679 --> 00:37:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] molila krunicu,

1011
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] a u drugoj ruci sam pripremala toplu vodu da te mogu poroditi.

1012
00:37:05,139 --> 00:37:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kaže,

1013
00:37:06,579 --> 00:37:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] od svega mi je bilo najteže to presići pupčanu vrbicu,

1014
00:37:10,159 --> 00:37:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] jer nijednom djetu nisam,

1015
00:37:11,199 --> 00:37:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] samo sebi moram prevezati pupčanu vrbicu,

1016
00:37:14,719 --> 00:37:18,340
[SPEAKER_01] i nijednom djetu nisam nikada vezala pupak

1017
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] i ne znam kako se to radi,

1018
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,820
[SPEAKER_01] kaže, ali ne mogu pust da umreš.

1019
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] A sad, možete mi sam iskala to snaga,

1020
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,820
[SPEAKER_01] da si sam doma,

1021
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] da rodiš djeta,

1022
00:37:25,559 --> 00:37:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] te sjećaš pupčanu vrbicu i sve.

1023
00:37:27,239 --> 00:37:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, uvijek sam slušao te njezine riječi,

1024
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] kak je to pričala.

1025
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ona nikad, nikada,

1026
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:33,360
[SPEAKER_01] nikoga nije osuđivala isto od sve,

1027
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:36,119
[SPEAKER_01] onaj rodbinu i sve one koje su inagovarali da me povaci.

1028
00:37:36,119 --> 00:37:38,239
[SPEAKER_01] Važno je da ih nije nikada slušala.

1029
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam mojeg slušao te njezine riječi,

1030
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] nikad nisam pričao tome nikdje javno,

1031
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] nikad ništa nisam govorio,

1032
00:37:45,239 --> 00:37:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] dok nisam došao na,

1033
00:37:48,059 --> 00:37:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] imao mladu misu.

1034
00:37:49,699 --> 00:37:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mlada misa vam je to kad se radi

1035
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] u tvojom rodnom kraju,

1036
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] nakon što postaneš svećenik

1037
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:56,800
[SPEAKER_01] i na kraju mlade mise imaš zahvalni govor.

1038
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ga pripremio večeras ovde da čujete,

1039
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] tada je bila prihoda,

1040
00:38:01,519 --> 00:38:03,539
[SPEAKER_01] zahvalim svojom mami što me nije pobacilo,

1041
00:38:03,539 --> 00:38:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] što sam oslo živ.

1042
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:06,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo, to je minuto,

1043
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću samo krenuti prema mojom laptopu,

1044
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] vi oznanite.

1045
00:38:08,619 --> 00:38:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ćemo se mi vratiti poslije,

1046
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] samo da poslušate taj dio.

1047
00:38:14,559 --> 00:38:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] Možda će malo odjekivati,

1048
00:38:21,659 --> 00:38:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali nadam se ćete čuti sve dobro.

1049
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:26,760
[UNKNOWN] Znači da se mi vrlo Boga.

1050
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:29,380
[UNKNOWN] I zato, to što vas,

1051
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,139
[UNKNOWN] kao svećenik svojim pred vama,

1052
00:38:31,139 --> 00:38:32,840
[UNKNOWN] zaista zbom milost,

1053
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:35,900
[UNKNOWN] upućujem i zahvalim Bogu,

1054
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:38,360
[UNKNOWN] jer se, kao kaželjstvo mnista,

1055
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:41,280
[SPEAKER_01] odpostavite komunist mladosti.

1056
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] Na drugom mjestu,

1057
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] želim zahvaliti svoje blake.

1058
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:49,380
